oem-mnzUKFklvfToEHKmYyV2yA">Trúc chi từ kỳ 04 - 竹枝詞其四</a> (<a href="https://www.thivien.net/V%C6%B0%C6%A1ng-Quang-Du%E1%BA%ABn/author-o4EVPW8qBqGIiDBnjz0VQg">Vương Quang Duẫn</a>)<br/>• <a target="_blank" href="https://www.thivien.net/H%E1%BB%93-Thi%C3%AAn-Du/Tu%C3%BD-ca-h%C3%A0nh/poem-6y9rj-YrWsH2nTdU8zPseA">Tuý ca hành - 醉歌行</a> (<a href="https://www.thivien.net/H%E1%BB%93-Thi%C3%AAn-Du/author-t5zNl0R6g-15oc9Dd33Eqg">Hồ Thiên Du</a>)<br/>• <a target="_blank" href="https://www.thivien.net/L%C3%BD-B%E1%BA%A1ch/U-gi%E1%BA%A3n-tuy%E1%BB%81n/poem-EWXqNfXDGvE8oGnx69xyyQ">U giản tuyền - 幽澗泉</a> (<a href="https://www.thivien.net/L%C3%BD-B%E1%BA%A1ch/author-8WYDeeki5xZo8eD-k6Sk5A">Lý Bạch</a>)<br/>• <a target="_blank" href="https://www.thivien.net/Ng%C3%B4-Th%C3%AC-Nh%E1%BA%ADm/Xu%C3%A2n-ng%C3%A2m/poem-Rfa7C6A_POegZiuLVghWiQ">Xuân ngâm - 春吟</a> (<a href="https://www.thivien.net/Ng%C3%B4-Th%C3%AC-Nh%E1%BA%ADm/author-14GcnhLjD2ajP0MTgtX13Q">Ngô Thì Nhậm</a>)<br/></div>	</div>
